original_title: SMTOWN LIVE 2022: SMCU EXPRESS @ HUMAN CITY_SUWON
overview: The festival moment that all people who have PINK BLOOD in have been waiting for!  SMTOWN Live 2022: SMCU Express@Human City Suwon is a joint Korean concert held by SM Entertainment artists (collectively known as SMTOWN). It was held on August 20, 2022, at Suwon World Cup Stadium in Suwon, South Korea. The concert was live-streamed via Beyond LIVE and KNTV.
tagline: NEXT STOP IS HUMAN CITY_SUWON, SUWON.
